Author: levelupgirl
Text: Careful, my friend started vaping to lose weight and now he’s just cripplingly addicted to nicotine and he can’t go 10 minutes without hitting his vape. The effects wear off too. Not worth :(

Author: billybathory
Text: Doesn't work! I've been vaping for 7+ years and it does not curb your appetite like analog cigarettes. Sorry to say!
